'''第47屆坎城影展'''於[[1994年電影|1994年]]5月12日（法國當地時間）至5月23日舉行。本屆[[坎城電影節|坎城影展]]評審團主席是[[美國|美國]][[演員|演員]][[克林·伊斯威特|克林·伊斯威特]]，[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]則由[[美國|美國]]導演[[昆汀·塔倫提諾|昆汀·塔倫提諾]]獲得<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1994-05-25/features/1994145031_1_quentin-tarantino-pulp-fiction-cannes-film-festivalp| title=Cannes' conclusion gives Eastwood a break, American filmmakers accolades|accessdate=10 December 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1994-05-24/entertainment/ca-61609_1_pulp-fiction|title=Surprise Pick: 'Pulp Fiction' : Cannes report: Quentin Tarantino's film is the third movie about the underbelly of American life to win the Palme d'Or in the last six years.|accessdate=10 December 2013|work=Los Angeles Times|first=Kenneth|last=Turan|date=24 May 1994|archive-date=2013-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218125746/http://articles.latimes.com/1994-05-24/entertainment/ca-61609_1_pulp-fiction|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/09/23/movies/film-festival-review-pulp-fiction-quentin-tarantino-s-wild-ride-life-s-dangerous.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|title=FILM FESTIVAL REVIEW: PULP FICTION; Quentin Tarantino's Wild Ride On Life's Dangerous Road|accessdate=10 December 2013|work=The New York Times|first=Janet|last=Maslin|date=23 September 1994|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106014909/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/09/23/movies/film-festival-review-pulp-fiction-quentin-tarantino-s-wild-ride-life-s-dangerous.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本屆坎城影展開幕片是[[柯恩兄弟|柯恩兄弟]]執導《{{link-en|金錢帝國|The Hudsucker Proxy}}》，閉幕片是[[約翰·華特斯|約翰·華特斯]]執導《{{link-en|瘋狂殺手俏媽咪|Serial Mom}}》（Serial Mom）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/cannes-great-opening-films/4.asp|title=Great Cannes Openers|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924052034/http://www.empireonline.com/features/cannes-great-opening-films/4.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1994-05-12/features/1994132161_1_hudsucker-proxy-pulp-fiction-competition|title=Fewer American films in Cannes competition|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129072324/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1994-05-12/features/1994132161_1_hudsucker-proxy-pulp-fiction-competition|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/05/24/movies/a-dark-comedy-wins-at-cannes.html|title=A Dark Comedy Wins at Cannes|accessdate=10 December 2013|work=The New York Times|first=Janet|last=Maslin|date=24 May 1994|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203000206/https://www.nytimes.com/1994/05/24/movies/a-dark-comedy-wins-at-cannes.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

